  "title": "Lab Assistant (Chemistry) / No experience needed - Training Provided (1 Year Contract) / Global MNC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is an US MNC, one of the largest players in the life-science sector. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting for Lab Assistant to be part of their team for ongoing transformation projects.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>This is a 1 Year contract (Convertible) role. They are located at Buona Vista – Walking distance from the MRT station.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>5 days work week - Monday to Friday (8.30 am to 5.30pm)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Training will be provided for Entry Level (structured training programs)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Duties</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare samples and reagents</li>\n  <li>Operate sample handling equipments</li>\n  <li>Ensure data accuracy and detail records</li>\n  <li>Adhere to safety procedures</li>\n  <li>Any other duties as assigned by supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimally Diploma in Chemistry / Lifescience / Biotech / Pharmacy / Food Tech related fields</li>\n  <li>No experience needed - Training Provided (structured training programs)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email Address: tc1@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Attention to: Alethea</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682<br>\nReg No: R21101676<br>\nNg Zhi Qing Alethea</p>",
